                <div class="writing paragraph text-grey text-left">You shoud wash your hands often with soap and water. This includes before and after eating and after going to the toilet. The key to handwashing is to wash often and wash well, for at least 20 seconds.  Use alcohol-based hand sanitisers when you can’t use soap and water.</div>
